text: The Château de Zuthove is a historic manor in Renescure, Nord, Nord-Pas-de- Calais, France. ==History== It was built in 1472.Les granges du Château de Zuthove ==Architectural significance== It has been listed as an official monument since 1946.French Ministry of Culture: Château de Zuthove ==References== Category:Châteaux in Nord (French department) Category:Houses completed in 1472 Category:Monuments historiques of Hauts-de-France
title: Château de Zuthove
